1.4
log
@Cope with the iscsid changes. Makes the msg handling a lot easier.
This also introduces some stuff that is work in progress.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: iscsictl.h,v 1.3 2014/04/20 22:22:18 claudio Exp $ */

/*
